The '''Spherical Flame''' was the sigil of the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] as of the [[Dorvalla Incident]] in [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]]. [[Dorvalla/Legends|Dorvallan]] transports ferrying cargo to the ''[[Revenue]]'' were emblazoned with this insignia.

